high_descs: Turn around and to the stand at the end of the counter.
Pick up the butter knife next to the lotion.
Slice the apple on the front right corner of the stand.
Move to the back corner of the stand on the left side.
Slice the apple on the back left corner of the stand.
Go to the microwave.
Put the knife in the microwave.
Go back to the stand at the end of the counter.
Pick up an apple slice from the front right corner.
Go to the microwave.
Put the apple slice in the microwave.
Go back to the stand at the end of the counter.
Pick up a slice of apple from the back left corner of the stand.
Take the apple slice to the microwave.
Put the slice of apple in the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put two slices of apple in the microwave.

high_descs: Turn around and go to the black stand.
Pick up the knife from the black stand.
Cut the yellow apple in the bottom right corner into three pieces.
Look up at the top of the table and then back down.
Cut the other yellow apple into three pieces.
Turn around, then make a left at the oven and go forward to the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the knife inside it and close it.
Walk back to the black stand.
Pick up the nearest slice of apple from the one on the bottom right corner.
Walk back to the microwave on the white table.
Open the microwave, put the apple slice inside in front of the handle part of the knife and close it.
Once again walk back to the black stand.
Pick up the nearest slice of apple from the one on the upper left corner.
Once again walk back to the microwave on the white table.
Open the microwave, put the apple slice inside in front of the blade part of the knife and close it.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife and two apple slices from different apples inside the microwave.

high_descs: Turn right until you face the dark brown 3 shelf unit and walk to it.
Take the knife from the dark brown 3 shelf unit.
Cut one of the apples on the the dark brown 3 shelf unit in three pieces.
Look up and reach for the other apple on the dark brown shelf.
Cut the other apple on the the dark brown 3 shelf unit in three pieces.
Turn around, walk towards the stove, then turn left, walk towards the trash can, then face the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the knife inside and close the microwave.
Turn left, move towards the fridge, then turn left again, move towards the stove, then turn right and walk to the dark brown 3 shelf unit.
Take one piece of apple from the dark brown 3 shelf unit.
Turn around, walk towards the stove, then turn left, walk towards the trash can, turn right and then face the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the apple slice inside and then close the microwave.
Turn left, move towards the fridge, then turn left again, move towards the stove, then turn right and walk to the dark brown 3 shelf unit.
Take one piece of the other apple from the dark brown 3 shelf unit.
Turn around, walk towards the stove, then turn left, walk towards the trash can, then face the microwave.
Open the microwave, put the apple slice inside and then close the microwave.
anns.task_desc: Put a knife and two apple slices in the microwave.
